node.text:
An action-packed day of topwater fishing has never been easier than when you tie on the Shimano Coltsniper Splash Walk. Hop in the boat with Capt. Jack @east_coast_charters as he breaks down lure color options, advantages of fishing the Splash Walk and best practices to ignite deafening explosions from giant striped bass this season.

Learn more about the Coltsniper Splash Walk and communicate with your local dealers about availability today by heading to our link in bio.

#FishShimano #ShimanoColtsniper #ColtsniperSplashWalk

node.text:
Our all-new muskie rod is up for grabs!  The 2020 SKIXX totally reinvents the premium muskie rod market!  Check with your local dealers for availability!  MSRP $399.99 @jimsaric_themuskyhunter 
#FishShimano #muskie #muskyfishing #chicagoland 
fish.shimano.com/skixx

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 11, 2021. May be an image of fishing rod and body of water.

node.text:
Improving upon the standard protection against corrosion, the Shimano Ultegra FC incorporates Shimano's X-Protect technology - a specially designed, water channeling, labyrinth construction -making it the ideal weapon for soldiers who operate on saltwater battlefields.

Which setup would you draw first: red or blue?

#FishShimano #ShimanoUltegra #UltegraFC

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 10, 2021. May be an image of body of water.

node.text:
The brand new Shimano World Minnow 115SP is a true show stopper. This lethal suspending jerkbait uses Shimano's patented Flash Boost technology to emit an enticing flash during the retrieve while mimicking a wounded baitfish on the pause. On days when slow cadence is the most crucial factor for securing a bite, the World Minnow 115SP ensures bass are taunted during every long pause.

#FishShimano #WorldMinnow #WorldMinnow115SP

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing in Florida with @captedzyakfishing. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
We've all skipped class to get in on a hot bite. That's why all Shimano School classes are recorded and available on-demand on the Shimano YouTube Channel. 

From discovering big snook tactics with @captedzyakfishing to a Canyons crash course with @east_coast_charters, there are two full seasons of in-depth #ShimanoSchool lessons available on the exclusive YouTube playlist.

Queue up your favorite class and take notes as the best in the business teach you everything you need to know for a successful trip on the water.

You can access the full library at our link in bio. 

#FishShimano #CloserToNature #ShimanoSchool

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 08, 2021.

node.text:
A fresh Shimano TwinPower SW waiting to get dressed up. The new TwinPower SW is a big game glutton. The 10000 and 14000 models incorporate Shimano's Heatsink Drag to deliver overwhelming drag performance by dissipating heat away from the spool to reduce drag-force drop caused by friction. The result: anglers can tangle with sea monsters without any fears of gear failure.

#FishShimano #ShimanoTwinPower #TwinPowerSW
📸: @tailwater_outfitters

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 07, 2021. May be a closeup.

node.text:
The little details can make the biggest difference. The Shimano CI4+ reel seat is constructed of material significantly lighter and more durable than conventional polymers. Shimano's ultralight reel seats increase rod sensitivity allowing anglers to maintain an intimate connection with their bait - and the fish that devour it.

#FishShimano #ShimanoRods #CI4Plus

node.text:
An action-packed day of topwater fishing has never been easier than when you tie on the Shimano Coltsniper Splash Walk. Hop in the boat with Capt. Jack @east_coast_charters as he breaks down lure color options, advantages of fishing the Splash Walk and best practices to ignite deafening explosions from giant striped bass this season.

Learn more about the Coltsniper Splash Walk and communicate with your local dealers about availability today by heading to our link in bio.

#FishShimano #ShimanoColtsniper #ColtsniperSplashWalk

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 05, 2021.

node.text:
Not all smallmouth are created equal. When in the presence of a "once in a lifetime" bronzeback, you can rely on the legendary Shimano Vanford to accurately present a bait in the strike zone and efficiently wrestle it to the side of the boat.

#FishShimano #ShimanoVanford #SmallmouthBass
📸: @carl_jocumsen

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 04, 2021. May be an image of fishing rod and body of water.

node.text:
The new Shimano Sustain features Silent Drive technology with extremely refined gearing tolerances throughout the entire drive train, eliminating the smallest clearance gaps and wobbles to provide smooth and quiet reeling.

Will you be adding a new Sustain to your arsenal this season?

#FishShimano #ShimanoSustain #Sustain

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Shimano North America Fishing on August 03, 2021 tagging @alexdavisfishing, and @jpderoseoutdoors. May be an image of one or more people, outdoors and text.

node.text:
Join @jpderoseoutdoors as he chats with Professional Angler & Lake Guntersville Guide @alexdavisfishing on tonight's edition of Shimano School!

To be a successful angler in the big leagues, you need to be able to adapt to rapidly changing conditions. The duo will discuss tackle versatility and how to dial in your approach with a variety of presentations and techniques.

Tune in tonight at 8PM EST via Shimano Facebook Live or Youtube Live. Head to our link in bio to set a reminder for tonight's class and tag a friend below who should tune in with you!

Shimano School is your chance to upgrade your angling knowledge and get questions answered from some of the best in the business! 

#ShimanoSchool #CloserToNature #FishShimano

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 02, 2021. May be an image of fishing rod.

node.text:
Now featuring Shimano's flagship Infinity Drive technology to improve pinion gear support and enhance the overall drive gear design, Spheros SW provides anglers with increased winding power under load when cranking against hard-fighting game fish. Spheros SW also boasts both X-Protect and X-Shield for improved water resistance for increased durability in the harsh saltwater environment - a necessary defense for hardcore inshore anglers.

#FishShimano #ShimanoSpheros #SpherosSW

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on August 01, 2021. May be an image of fishing rod and body of water.

node.text:
The Shimano Teramar XX SE casting rods set a new standard in performance with technique-specific powers, actions and features for fishing the myriad of inshore game fish in the southeast region of the United States. From slow-rolling swimbaits along dock pilings to working topwater plugs next to a sea wall, Teramar XX SE casting rods are ready to entice and tame saltwater behemoths.

#FishShimano #ShimanoTeramar #TermarXXSE

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Shimano North America Fishing on July 31, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and nature.

node.text:
Loaded with flagship features, Shimano's Exsence provides bass anglers with everything they need in a featherweight package. The magnesium HAGANE Body offers rigidity and all-day comfort when trying to lure giant smallmouth from their deep water haunts. Additionally, the MGL Rotor provides smallie addicts better balance and requires less inertia to start and stop, making for an extremely smooth angling experience.

What do you think this pair of bronze beasts weighed?

#FishShimano #BassFishing #ShimanoExsence
📸: @spenser_samplawski
